Changes in version 0.7-0
------------------------

- added data set from Wittmann et al. (2014)

- added data set from Montero-Calasanz et al. (2013)


Changes in version 0.6-0
------------------------

- formal improvements as required by new CRAN restrictions


Changes in version 0.5-0
------------------------

- updated binary data (no user-visible changes)


Changes in version 0.4-0
------------------------

- updated aggregation and discretisation settings to the new style; as this
  causes incompatibilities, 'opmdata' >= 0.4-0 should only be used in
  conjunction with 'opm' > 0.7-0


Changes in version 0.3-0
------------------------

- some aesthetical improvements of the documentation


Changes in version 0.2-0
------------------------

- included discretised values
- improved documentation
- nicer package URL


Changes in version 0.1-0
------------------------

- initial release on CRAN

